Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong. Hina?\NThat's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ladybug Bush (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These were the circumstances.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}There was bullying going on in Hina's class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It began suddenly in April,\Nwhen the now third-year classes switched,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}splitting up into groups\Nbased on names in alphabetical order.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I. Told. You. Stop following us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The victim was scared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and bewildered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It started a vicious circle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The girl's name was Chiho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She and Hina were classmates\Nsince elementary school{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and always gotten along well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chiho was a really cute, kind,\Nand quiet girl who always smiled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The third year began,\Nand entrance exams were looming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When everyone was in the grip\Nof a nameless anxiety,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they said she was flirting with boys,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or acting like a goody-goody\Nin front of the teacher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For vague reasons like these,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they began to ostracize her from their group.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chiho recoiled and in response,\Nthe girls in the group shunned her even more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone else was afraid of that group\Nand just looked on from a distance,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but of course,\NHina couldn't do something like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was too fond of this girl who\Nshe was friends with since elementary school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you cleaning all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, they said they had things to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are the pajamas we have to do\Nfor home economics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing home\Neveryone else's, Chiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For six people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not what you think.\NI volunteered to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk to the teacher about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't tell the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone found out,\Nthey would bully me even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, please! Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But little by little, the situation escalated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One shoe is missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bag too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other shoe was dropped in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chiho had a lot of absences\Nfrom school after that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're misreading it, Ms. Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The girls in that group\Nare just playing harmless pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't turn\Nevery situation into a bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Na more positive girl, Ms. Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her teacher, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, you shouldn't get involved with Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They might target you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And her classmates, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh?\N- Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had my hands full\Npreparing for entrance exams this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They all pretended\Nthat they didn't see anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, finally...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is sudden, but Ms. Sakura is moving\Nto another school due to family circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'd stopped going to school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so her mother decided they would move\Nto Iwate, where Chiho's father was working.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After everything you've done for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B Group is short one person.\NWhere's Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Teacher, Sakura changed schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? This late in the year?\NAnd so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I hear they suddenly decided to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, really, who would go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry. Hina, I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kawamoto!\NKnock it off, Kawamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they next set their sights...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on Hina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, what should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chiho was crying. She said she was afraid\Nto switch to another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}She said, "What if I get bullied over there too?"\NShe was terrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do anything to help Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Not one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I-I'm going for a run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Hina! Don't go outside! It's dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't go!\N- I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,School was so fun to go to every day\Nuntil the second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chiho was so stressed with everything,\Nso why did everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,pretend they didn't see anything or like,\N"If you protect her, they'll target you next."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But things turned out\Nthe way they said it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From tomorrow, I'll be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I've been scared this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret anything at all! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...what I did was definitely not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that moment,\Nas I saw her declare that through sobs,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it felt like I was struck by lightning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even after...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so much time has passed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}something can save you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}coming in like a storm\Nfrom a completely different direction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Even if it takes the rest of my life,\NI will pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladybug Bush (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ladybug Bush (Part 3)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on the way back home from school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei was sitting on a bench...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}next to the bridge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"There's something I want to research,\Nso I was hoping you can take me to the library."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what Rei said, so I led the way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hadn't been to the library\Nsince elementary school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I saw the chairs in the kids' corner,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it made me think, "Were we that small?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and tears came to my eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}Book of Manju\NEasy Sweets\NBasics of Traditional Sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"They had all of these."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As Rei said that, he brought over\Nseveral books of beautiful sweets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Traditional Sweets\NRecommended Japanese-style Sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd seen some of the sweets before\Nat Grandpa's shop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were also many pretty sweets\NI never even knew about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Rei sat next to me,\Ngazing at field guides on plants and insects.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was called a "silverthorn."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what I've always called\Na two-starred ladybug is actually named
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Harmonia axyridis."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The characters for ladybug\Nare "Heavenly Path Insect"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}When I muttered that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It keeps climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It took off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As we watched the ladybug fly away,\NRei explained to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that the Japanese name is from long ago,\Nwhen people pointed at this cute little creature,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as it flew towards the sun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how it got its name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladybug Bush (Part 3)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While she gripped my sleeve and cried,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my whole body throbbed\Nas if it had become one heart,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it was so painful that it felt like\Nit wanted to tear me apart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that moment, I wanted to hunt down\Nthe people who made her cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and rip them limb from limb,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but that wouldn't solve the problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That wouldn't benefit her at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So think. Think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, when we got back to her house...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just finished making dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, Rei, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You went to the library?\NWith Rei? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, come on in as well, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was Akari and Momo, the same as usual,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a warm dinner served on a low dining table,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and a grim-looking Grandpa, waiting for her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Hina, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Akari told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.43,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PAW PAW
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SUICIDE, VICTIM WAS BULLIED
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even I know how nasty bullying is after seeing it\Nin newspapers and on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BULLYING BEHIND SUICIDES, RISING
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}140,000 CASES OF BULLYING
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SCHOOLS BEING NEGLIGENT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}Teacher Responses:\N"Don't rock the boat."\N"Do you feel bad about it?"\NBully Responses:\NClick their tongue when I go by
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}When Bullied Students Speak Up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}"They put junk in my food."\NGirl changes schools after bullying
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bullying Countermeasures Commission
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I see it in the news,\Nit breaks me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And yet you tried to help your friend\Nout of a scary situation like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That took real courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not many adults could've done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm proud of you, granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do a single thing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You helped your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, we all had dinner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa told me,\N"Thanks for going after Hina last night."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Now eat up,"\Nand he slapped me on the back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hina ate a lot too,\Nthough she was crying the whole time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We had deep-fried chicken,\Npotato salad, and cream stew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akari made all the food that Hina loves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I chewed, I continuously searched my brain\Nfor something I could do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.93,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 27
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can take your time on this,\Nso listen patiently to their thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must honorably repay gratitude.\NThat is the way of things for humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.94,0:24:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally willing to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.36,0:24:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Nikaidou!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm a guy after all, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.78,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really no good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:58.33,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ILLUSTRATOR:\NTSUNAMI UMINO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.03,0:24:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry-meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.99,0:24:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want some fried chicken-meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.20,0:24:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Potato salad is good too-meow.
